title: Democracy 2 v1.25
description:
Think you're the next great political ruler? It's time to put your political know-how through the ringer as you govern a country and make the calls when it comes to health care, education, and social welfare. Choose from a variety of scenarios - will you turn a debt-ridden state into one of wealth or bring down the world's only remaining superpower? Democracy 2 is the political strategy game that will have you balancing every decision you make and scrambling to fix the consequences.

System Requirements

OS: Windows XP or later
Processor: Pentium 2
Memory: 1 GB
Graphics: 64 MB VRAM
